title: The Comfort of Home is Within Your Reach – New 3 Bedroom Home!
posting_body: ['SUMMER SPECIAL:', 'Rent a brand-new Oaks Landing apartment home this summer to lock in 2021 rent rates and save hundreds of dollars every month!*', '*Some restrictions may apply.', 'Offer valid when you move-in by 8/31/2022.', 'Please call for more details.', 'Oaks Landing is a BRAND-NEW affordable community for active 55+ adults!', 'Offering a variety of spacious studio, 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartment homes, we are experts at combining quality and comfort, making Oaks Landing an ideal place to call home.', 'Residents of our community get to enjoy a wide variety of spectacular amenities.', "From the gorgeous courtyard and lounge spaces to impressive picnic areas perfect for barbecues, we've made sure there is something for everyone.", 'Make this community your new home and enjoy our modern, state-of-the-art fitness center, underground parking lot, cards/crafts room, beauty salon, and beautiful community room with Wi-Fi access & a toasty fireplace.', 'So, look no further, your new apartment home awaits!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Water, sewer and trash removal services', 'included', '- Heated, underground parking garage', '- Cards and crafts room', '- Open summer 2022 - brand-new affordable community!', '- Business center', '- Energy Star kitchen appliance package', '- 24-Hour emergency maintenance', '- Storage lockers', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Oaks Landing is a 55 or better senior community and participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community, credit, public record & rental background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Oaks Landing', '700 7th Street, NW.', 'New Brighton, MN, 55112', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'sAsg5daqI2k']
